UMENGAMELI wakuleli, uMnuz Cyril Ramaphosa, uzwe usizi lwabantu bakuleli ebambezeleka egibele isitimela ePitoli ngoMsombuluko ekuseni. URamaphosa ugibele isitimela sakwaMetro Rail nezinye izikhulu ze-ANC njengengxenye yomkhankaso we-ANC njengoba kubhekwe okhethweni. URamaphosa nalezi zikhulu bebehlele ukungena esitimeleni banxene abavoti ukuthi bavotele iqembu elibusayo. Ngokohlelo uRamaphosa, bekumele agibele isitimela eMabopane Station ngo-6.30 ekuseni kodwa walinda isikhathi esingangehora ngaphambi kokuthi angene kuso. Uthe esengena ngo-7.30, wabhekana nezinkinga abantu bakuleli ababhekana nazo zinsuku zonke. To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web browser that
    supports HTML5 video This is a modal window. Beginning of dialog window. Escape will cancel and close the window. End of dialog window. Ngaphakathi abagibeli bazise uRamaphosa ngezinkinga zabo okubalwa kuzo ukungagcini isikhathi kwezitimela, abanye babeka izimpilo zabo engcupheni ukuze bakwazi ukugibela. Abanye abebelinde eBosman Station kusukela ngo-5 ekuseni bathe bazofika emsebenzini sesidulile isikhathi ngenxa yokungafiki ngesikhathi kwesitimela. URamaphosa uthe ujabule ngokukwazi ukubona ukuthi abantu bakuleli babhekana nobunzima obunjani ezitimeleni. Uthembise abagibeli ukuthi i-ANC izothuthukisa ukusebenza kwezitimela kuleli maduze.